{"tid":1752584,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實呢個結果係不嬲都有機會出現","createTime":"2019-11-24T21:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T04:10:22.000Z","uid":12185,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"777be5ae89d573fa5a67a9dc56daedc4e9ea7387","tid":1752584,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T21:45:45.000Z","msg":"從來建制輸嘅關鍵就只有一個：高投票率。<br />\n呢個定律係放諸四海皆準，民主國家都係咁<br />\n高投票率，代表更多年輕人出黎投票，反對黨就更大贏面。<br />\n呢個結果其實不嬲都有可能出現，只係以前好多人唔肯出黎投票。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/images/small_VT_HK_c.jpg?20191124222136\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Fdc2019%2Fimages%2Fsmall_VT_HK_c.jpg%3F20191124222136&h=f7e0f6cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5aced53ba5ecf35fdce97847612c502d26770821","tid":1752584,"uid":161404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T21:49:39.000Z","msg":"其實我都知道阿媽係女人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ecb78e1a8097c526a8820e7150e0ec93e772b4","tid":1752584,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:08:44.000Z","msg":"勿忘受傷及被捕手足，以區議會大勝為基礎繼續抗爭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1752548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1752548</a>"},{"pid":"4875d63e92e1d596dea6f73dfd6b83ac381e55d7","tid":1752584,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aced53ba5ecf35fdce97847612c502d26770821","tid":1752584,"uid":161404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T21:49:39.000Z","msg":"其實我都知道阿媽係女人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:10:22.000Z","msg":"主要問題係高投票率呢樣野係從來大家都有能力做到<br />\n冇成本，非常易做，行出街吸個印<br />\n但要去到大量手足被斬被殺爆眼中槍先move到大家出黎投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢次個勝利我地不嬲都應該擁有只係大家連投票都唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}